Theres a workaround for the issue. When you create the gyro, use

new ADIS16448_IMU(ADIS16448_IMU.IMUAxis.kZ, SPI.Port.kMXP, ADIS16448_IMU.CalibrationTime._1s);

intead of the parameterless constructor.
